question: Imagine the post credits of Spider-Man Far From Home is Peter arriving home revealing Carol and an man named Genis (Bryan Dechart) talking with a scared Aunt May as she is surrounded by Bucky, Valkyrie, Scott, Bruce, Sam, and Hope with Carol saying that Peter is in danger right now. Cue Peter asking what's going on as Genis uses a Skrull detector on him as Aunt May hugs him telling Peter he needs to go and pack his things with Carol saying the Avengers have been compromised.

tags: it is canon that peter can't drive
summary: The Real Reason Spidey Can't Drive (superfamily imagine)
body:
The Real Reason Spidey Can’t Drive (superfamily imagine)

Steve (instructing 15 year old son): Everyone needs to learn how to drive

Tony: I don’t think this is a good idea

Peter: Yeah, pops, I don’t really want….hey do you see that bee? *leaps out of car in traffic and chases bee*

S: He’s going to get stung

T: You know your son better that that, he’s going to make friends

Peter (rushing back, bee cradled carefully in his hands): Hey! Wanna hold him?

T: Told ya

S: *holds it, gets stung*

summary: 100 followers special I can’t believe that we made it to 100 followers! Thank you so much to everyone that helped by liking,...
body:
100 followers special

I can’t believe that we made it to 100 followers! Thank you so much to everyone that helped by liking, reblogging, and of course, following. 

To celebrate, I thought it would be fun to write blurbs + oneshots inspired from some prompts I found online. 

— To submit a request, message me any character ( i usually post borhap + queen and marvel but you can submit anything you’d like), 

a reader description (this is optional), 

and the prompt number (feel free to send in multiple prompts + feel free to add in a description of what exactly you might want.)

Enjoy x 

PROMPTS

1. “Are you trying to seduce me into healthy sleeping patterns?”

2. “I think you’re mildly decent.”

3. “I didn’t come here to argue.” 

4. “Your idea of fun always breaks the law. Why can’t we just go get a pizza or something?”

5. “Can I hide behind you? Thanks.”

6. “So, was it worth it?”

7. “Can we pretend nothing happened here?”

8. “I’m not going anywhere.”

9. “Don’t look at me like that, I wasn’t the one who got us in this mess.”

10. “Oh! I get it now! You’re just a dumbass!”

11.  “Be nice, please? Just this once, for me.”

12. “What’s that look for? Did I do something wrong?”

13. “I wish I could visit you more–I do. I’ve just been really … busy.”

14. “This party sucks. Wanna go somewhere?”

15. “Leave them out of this!” 

16. “You are so dumb, I love you.”

17. “Can I have this dance?”

18. “Stop sending me heart emojis at midnight.”

19. “My feather boa is my greatest achievement.”

20. “Hey loser! I love you and your face!”

—Just a little disclaimer, I don’t write smut lol sorry my dudes

I can’t believe that we made it to 100 followers! Thank you so much to everyone that helped by liking, reblogging, and of course, following. 

To celebrate, I thought it would be fun to write blurbs + oneshots inspired from some prompts I found online. 

— To submit a request, message me any character ( i usually post borhap + queen and marvel but you can submit anything you’d like), 

a reader description (this is optional), 

and the prompt number (feel free to send in multiple prompts + feel free to add in a description of what exactly you might want.)

Enjoy x 

PROMPTS

1. “Are you trying to seduce me into healthy sleeping patterns?”

2. “I think you’re mildly decent.”

3. “I didn’t come here to argue.” 

4. “Your idea of fun always breaks the law. Why can’t we just go get a pizza or something?”

5. “Can I hide behind you? Thanks.”

6. “So, was it worth it?”

7. “Can we pretend nothing happened here?”

8. “I’m not going anywhere.”

9. “Don’t look at me like that, I wasn’t the one who got us in this mess.”

10. “Oh! I get it now! You’re just a dumbass!”

11.  “Be nice, please? Just this once, for me.”

12. “What’s that look for? Did I do something wrong?”

13. “I wish I could visit you more–I do. I’ve just been really … busy.”

14. “This party sucks. Wanna go somewhere?”

15. “Leave them out of this!” 

16. “You are so dumb, I love you.”

17. “Can I have this dance?”

18. “Stop sending me heart emojis at midnight.”

19. “My feather boa is my greatest achievement.”

20. “Hey loser! I love you and your face!”

—Just a little disclaimer, I don’t write smut lol sorry my dudes
